CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

January 21, 2004

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2003-1598. Schirmer v. Brown Cty. Court of Common Pleas, Div. of Domestic Relations.

In Prohibition. On motion to dismiss amended complaint. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor and O’Donnell, JJ., concur.
